<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:49:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>风险事件频发，日元为日本央行决定做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-braces-boj-decision-with-risk-events-aplenty-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三，在日本央行 (BOJ) 做出关键政策决定之前，日元徘徊在 2-1/2 个月高点附近，日本央行将详细说明缩减巨额债券购买规模的计划，并可能加息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-braces-boj-decision-with-risk-events-aplenty-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜称数千房屋遭受洪水袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/north-korea-says-thousands-homes-hit-by-flooding-2024-07-30/</link><description>官方媒体朝中社周三称，由于强降雨，朝鲜新义州市和靠近中国边境的义州县有 4000 多所房屋被淹。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/north-korea-says-thousands-homes-hit-by-flooding-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>力拓半年利润符合预期，预计中国需求良好</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rio-tinto-reports-largely-flat-first-half-profit-2024-07-30/</link><description>力拓周三公布的半年基本盈利增长符合市场预期，因为其主要商品铁矿石价格的下跌被铜和铝业务的增长所抵消。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rio-tinto-reports-largely-flat-first-half-profit-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：今年市场最重要的一天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-30/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 21:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪探索进入加拿大汽车市场-监管备案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-explores-canadian-auto-market-entry-regulatory-filing-2024-07-30/</link><description>根据本月早些时候提交的一份监管文件，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪正在寻求进入加拿大汽车市场，尽管加拿大官员正在考虑对从中国进口的汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:19:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-explores-canadian-auto-market-entry-regulatory-filing-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国和美国的拖拉销售，星巴克效率提高提振利润</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-quarterly-global-sales-drop-larger-than-expected-china-weakness-2024-07-30/</link><description>星巴克门店运营的改善帮助​​这家咖啡连锁店满足了华尔街对季度利润的预期，尽管其全球销售额因美国和中国主要市场消费者支出持续疲软而下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-quarterly-global-sales-drop-larger-than-expected-china-weakness-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官预计印度与乌克兰有更多接触</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-diplomat-expects-more-indian-engagement-with-ukraine-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二在参议院听证会上回答有关印度总理莫迪本月访问莫斯科的问题时表示，他预计很快就会有消息称印度正在加强与乌克兰的接触。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 17:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-diplomat-expects-more-indian-engagement-with-ukraine-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球-中国金牌得主王的喜悦因狗仔队拍球事故而中断</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-china-gold-medalist-wangs-joy-cut-short-by-paparazzi-paddle-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，中国24岁的乒乓球运动员王楚钦与队友孙颖莎一起夺得了自己的第一枚奥运会金牌，他欣喜若狂。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-china-gold-medalist-wangs-joy-cut-short-by-paparazzi-paddle-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧莱雅二季度销量上升但中国市场低迷承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-2q-sales-grow-53-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-30/</link><description>法国化妆品巨头欧莱雅公布第二季度销售额增长 5.3%，低于预期，这可能进一步令本已担心重要的中国市场缺乏反弹的投资者感到不安。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-2q-sales-grow-53-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>二号外交官表示，美国必须采取更多措施反击中国的行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二表示，华盛顿必须采取更多措施来对抗中国的行动，包括其建立军事基地的战略以及在非洲开采稀土矿的战略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国对伊朗导弹和无人机计划支持者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-sanctions-targeting-irans-missile-drone-program-facilitators-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国周二对五名个人和七个实体实施制裁，财政部称这些人是伊朗导弹和无人机计划的协助者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-sanctions-targeting-irans-missile-drone-program-facilitators-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球——中国队东京失利后王健林和孙杨夺得混双金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-wang-sun-win-mixed-doubles-gold-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，在巴黎奥运会乒乓球混双决赛中，中国组合王楚钦/孙颖莎以4比2击败朝鲜组合李钟植/金锦勇，这是中国队横扫乒乓球项目金牌的第一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-wang-sun-win-mixed-doubles-gold-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>审计员称，奢华的国宴使法国总统陷入赤字</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavish-state-banquets-tip-french-presidency-into-red-auditor-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>公共审计办公室表示，法国总统马克龙的办公室去年因取消为英国国王查尔斯举办的豪华龙虾晚宴和其他国宴而超支了数百万欧元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:58:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavish-state-banquets-tip-french-presidency-into-red-auditor-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>Grifols 对中国投资减记 4.94 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-revises-past-financial-records-with-equity-value-drop-494-mln-2024-07-30/</link><description>西班牙制药商 Grifols 已对其 2020 年至 2023 年的账目进行了 4.57 亿欧元（4.94 亿美元）的减记，以反映其所称的之前对其持有的中国上海莱士股份的会计处理不正确的情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-revises-past-financial-records-with-equity-value-drop-494-mln-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国表示对中国征收新关税将至少推迟两周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-start-new-china-tariffs-will-be-delayed-by-least-two-weeks-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国贸易代表办公室周二表示，美国对电动汽车及其电池、计算机芯片和医疗产品等一系列中国进口产品大幅提高关税的部分举措将至少推迟两周。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-start-new-china-tariffs-will-be-delayed-by-least-two-weeks-2024-07-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>